{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887224444,"sessionID":"ses_284df9b52ffe1wc49UbpN6zfYj","part":{"id":"prt_d7b2087bf001J8SS34LorT592f","messageID":"msg_d7b207605001egTJx6Dkx6SW7M","sessionID":"ses_284df9b52ffe1wc49UbpN6zfYj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_4005b51b1e9645c5bd23a77b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: The purpose of this proposal is to create comprehensive architecture design documentation and API documentation for the AgentCube project. This documentation will:\n6: \n7: 1. Provide detailed architectural diagrams and component descriptions for the SDK and runtime system\n8: 2. Document all public APIs for the Python SDK, including client classes, services, and CLI commands\n9: 3. Establish a single source of truth for developers integrating with AgentCube\n10: 4. Enable faster onboarding for new team members and external developers\n11: 5. Support the existing Docusaurus documentation framework established in AR-042\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: ### In scope\n16: \n17: | Item | Detail |\n18: |------|--------|\n19: | **Module path** | `docs` |\n20: | **Language** | Markdown (via Docusaurus) |\n21: | **Documentation type** | Architecture design + API reference |\n22: \n23: ### Architectural Documentation\n24: \n25: | Document | Description |\n26: |----------|-------------|\n27: | `docs/docs/architecture/system-design.md` | System-level architecture with component interactions |\n28: | `docs/docs/architecture/client-sdk.md` | SDK client architecture (AgentRuntimeClient, CodeInterpreterClient) |\n29: | `docs/docs/architecture/services.md` | Service layer architecture (MetadataService, DockerService, K8sProvider) |\n30: | `docs/docs/architecture/runtime.md` | Runtime operations architecture (Pack, Build, Publish, Invoke, Status) |\n31: | `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow.md` | Data flow diagrams and sequence diagrams |\n32: \n33: ### API Documentation\n34: \n35: | Document | Description |\n36: |----------|-------------|\n37: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-agent-runtime.md` | AgentRuntimeClient SDK API |\n38: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-code-interpreter.md` | CodeInterpreterClient SDK API |\n39: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-services.md` | Service layer APIs |\n40: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-runtime.md` | Runtime operation APIs |\n41: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-exceptions.md` | Exception reference |\n42: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-cli.md` | CLI command reference |\n43: \n44: ### Out of scope\n45: \n46: - Backend API documentation (Router, Control Plane, Data Plane endpoints)\n47: - Deployment and infrastructure documentation\n48: - User guides and tutorials (covered in existing docs)\n49: - Internal implementation details not exposed via public API\n50: \n51: ### Dependencies\n52: \n53: | Dependency | Usage |\n54: |------------|-------|\n55: | Docusaurus 3.x | Documentation framework (from AR-042) |\n56: | Existing `docs/docs/guides/architecture.md` | Current architecture content to be expanded |\n57: | Existing `docs/docs/api/*` | Current API docs to be replaced/enhanced |\n58: | Mermaid.js | Diagram rendering in Markdown |\n59: \n60: ## Design\n61: \n62: ### Directory structure additions\n63: \n64: ```\n65: docs/\n66: └── docs/\n67:     ├── architecture/           # New architecture docs\n68:     │   ├── system-design.md\n69:     │   ├── client-sdk.md\n70:     │   ├── services.md\n71:     │   ├── runtime.md\n72:     │   └── data-flow.md\n73:     └── api/\n74:         ├── sdk-agent-runtime.md\n75:         ├── sdk-code-interpreter.md\n76:         ├── sdk-services.md\n77:         ├── sdk-runtime.md\n78:         ├── sdk-exceptions.md\n79:         └── sdk-cli.md\n80: ```\n81: \n82: ### Architecture documentation format\n83: \n84: ```markdown\n85: # Component Name\n86: \n87: ## Overview\n88: \n89: Brief description of the component's purpose and responsibilities.\n90: \n91: ## Architecture Diagram\n92: \n93: ```mermaid\n94: graph TB\n95:     A[Client] --> B[Router]\n96:     B --> C[Agent Runtime]\n97: ```\n98: \n99: ## Key Classes/Functions\n100: \n101: ### ClassName\n102: \n103: | Property/Method | Type | Description |\n104: |-----------------|------|-------------|\n105: | `param` | `str` | Description |\n106: \n107: ## Initialization\n108: \n109: ```python\n110: from agentcube import ClassName\n111: \n112: client = ClassName(param=\"value\")\n113: ```\n114: \n115: ## Use Cases\n116: \n117: 1. Use case 1\n118: 2. Use case 2\n119: ```\n120: \n121: ### API documentation format\n122: \n123: ```markdown\n124: # SDK API Reference\n125: \n126: ## ClassName\n127: \n128: ### Constructor\n129: \n130: ```python\n131: ClassName(param1: str, param2: int = 10)\n132: ```\n133: \n134: | Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n135: |-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n136: | param1 | str | Required | Description |\n137: \n138: ### Methods\n139: \n140: #### method_name\n141: \n142: ```python\n143: client.method_name(arg1: str) -> dict\n144: ```\n145: \n146: **Parameters:**\n147: \n148: | Name | Type | Description |\n149: |------|------|-------------|\n150: | arg1 | str | Description |\n151: \n152: **Returns:** `dict` - Description\n153: \n154: **Raises:** `ExceptionType` - When condition\n155: \n156: **Example:**\n157: \n158: ```python\n159: result = client.method_name(\"value\")\n160: ```\n161: \n162: ## Exceptions\n163: \n164: | Exception | Description |\n165: |-----------|-------------|\n166: | `AgentCubeError` | Base exception |\n167: ```\n168: \n169: ### Sidebar updates\n170: \n171: ```typescript\n172: // sidebars.ts addition\n173: {\n174:   type: 'category',\n175:   label: 'Architecture',\n176:   items: [\n177:     'architecture/system-design',\n178:     'architecture/client-sdk',\n179:     'architecture/services',\n180:     'architecture/runtime',\n181:     'architecture/data-flow',\n182:   ],\n183: },\n184: {\n185:   type: 'category',\n186:   label: 'SDK API Reference',\n187:   items: [\n188:     'api/sdk-agent-runtime',\n189:     'api/sdk-code-interpreter',\n190:     'api/sdk-services',\n191:     'api/sdk-runtime',\n192:     'api/sdk-exceptions',\n193:     'api/sdk-cli',\n194:   ],\n195: },\n196: ```\n197: \n198: ## Impact analysis\n199: \n200: ### Files created\n201: \n202: | File | Description |\n203: |------|-------------|\n204: | `docs/docs/architecture/system-design.md` | System architecture (~150 lines) |\n205: | `docs/docs/architecture/client-sdk.md` | SDK client architecture (~200 lines) |\n206: | `docs/docs/architecture/services.md` | Services architecture (~150 lines) |\n207: | `docs/docs/architecture/runtime.md` | Runtime operations (~150 lines) |\n208: | `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow.md` | Data flow diagrams (~100 lines) |\n209: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-agent-runtime.md` | AgentRuntimeClient API (~250 lines) |\n210: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-code-interpreter.md` | CodeInterpreterClient API (~300 lines) |\n211: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-services.md` | Services API (~200 lines) |\n212: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-runtime.md` | Runtime API (~200 lines) |\n213: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-exceptions.md` | Exceptions reference (~100 lines) |\n214: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-cli.md` | CLI reference (~200 lines) |\n215: \n216: **Estimated total**: ~1800 lines\n217: \n218: ### Files modified\n219: \n220: | File | Change |\n221: |------|--------|\n222: | `docs/sidebars.ts` | Add architecture and SDK API categories |\n223: | `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` | Add Mermaid support if needed |\n224: \n225: ### Dependencies\n226: \n227: | Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n228: |------------|---------|---------|\n229: | mermaid | ^10.0.0 | Diagram rendering |\n230: | @docusaurus/theme-mermaid | ^3.0.0 | Mermaid plugin for Docusaurus |\n231: \n232: ### Downstream consumers\n233: \n234: | Consumer | Dependency |\n235: |----------|-----------|\n236: | SDK users | Reference for integration |\n237: | Internal developers | Understanding architecture |\n238: | External contributors | Onboarding and contribution |\n239: | Technical writers | Maintain documentation |\n240: \n241: ### Breaking change risk\n242: \n243: **Very Low**: This is documentation-only work. No code changes are made. Existing documentation remains accessible alongside new content.\n244: \n245: ### Performance characteristics\n246: \n247: - **Build time impact**: Minimal (~5-10 seconds for new docs)\n248: - **Static site size**: ~1-2MB additional for diagrams\n249: - **Rendering**: Mermaid diagrams render client-side\n250: \n251: ### Edge cases handled\n252: \n253: 1. **Missing diagrams**: Graceful fallback with link to source\n254: 2. **Code examples**: Tested against actual SDK code\n255: 3. **API changes**: Documentation follows code conventions from source\n256: 4. **Cross-references**: Internal links between related docs\n257: \n258: ## Alternatives considered\n259: \n260: ### 1. Auto-generate from docstrings using pdoc/sphinx\n261: \n262: **Approach**: Use automated documentation generation from Python docstrings.\n263: \n264: **Rejected because**:\n265: - Generates API reference only, no architectural overview\n266: - Doesn't integrate with Docusaurus theme\n267: - Limited customization for different audiences\n268: - Requires additional tooling setup\n269: \n270: ### 2. Use OpenAPI/Swagger for API docs\n271: \n272: **Approach**: Define API contracts in OpenAPI spec and generate docs.\n273: \n274: **Rejected because**:\n275: - Primary API is Python SDK, not HTTP REST\n276: - CLI docs not covered by OpenAPI\n277: - Additional infrastructure needed for spec management\n278: - Less readable for SDK users\n279: \n280: ### 3. Use TypeDoc for JavaScript SDK documentation\n281: \n282: **Approach**: Use TypeDoc for generating JavaScript-focused API docs.\n283: \n284: **Rejected because**:\n285: - AgentCube SDK is Python-based\n286: - Doesn't integrate with existing Docusaurus\n287: - No support for architecture diagrams\n288: - Different audience from TypeScript developers\n289: \n290: ### 4. Use Sphinx with Read the Docs\n291: \n292: **Approach**: Use Sphinx (Python documentation tool) with Read the Docs.\n293: \n294: **Rejected because**:\n295: - Duplicates documentation framework (Docusaurus from AR-042)\n296: - Team expertise in Docusaurus/MDX\n297: - Less flexible theming\n298: - Multiple documentation sites\n299: \n300: ### 5. Focus only on REST API documentation\n301: \n302: **Approach**: Document only the HTTP API, not SDK.\n303: \n304: **Rejected because**:\n305: - Primary integration point is Python SDK\n306: - SDK provides better developer experience\n307: - CLI needs separate documentation\n308: - Incomplete coverage for users\n\n(End of file - total 308 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n\n## Purpose\n\nThe purpose of this proposal is to create comprehensive architecture design documentation and API documentation for the AgentCube project. This documentation will:\n\n1. Provide detailed architectural diagrams and component descriptions for the SDK and runtime system\n2. Document all public APIs for the Python SDK, including client classes, services, and CLI commands\n3. Establish a single source of truth for developers integrating with AgentCube\n4. Enable faster onboarding for new team members and external developers\n5. Support the existing Docusaurus documentation framework established in AR-042\n\n## Scope\n\n### In scope\n\n| Item | Detail |\n|------|--------|\n| **Module path** | `docs` |\n| **Language** | Markdown (via Docusaurus) |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775887224425,"end":1775887224443}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887224447,"sessionID":"ses_284df9b52ffe1wc49UbpN6zfYj","part":{"id":"prt_d7b208b5a001npsox3vXxer4Ek","messageID":"msg_d7b207605001egTJx6Dkx6SW7M","sessionID":"ses_284df9b52ffe1wc49UbpN6zfYj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_2bcf78dc65fa4a15aaf52fef","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing a Docusaurus documentation site framework for the AgentCube project.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-042\n10: - **Module**: `docs`\n11: - **Language**: TypeScript\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Background\n17: \n18: AgentCube 需要一个现代化的文档站点来承载项目文档、API 参考、教程等内容。Docusaurus 是 Facebook 开发的开源静态网站生成器，专为技术文档设计，支持 Markdown、React 组件嵌入、版本管理和全文搜索等特性。\n19: \n20: docs 模块将作为独立的前端模块，位于项目根目录下的 `docs/` 目录，包含完整的 Docusaurus 配置和内容结构。\n21: \n22: ---\n23: \n24: ## Requirements\n25: \n26: ### Feature: 项目初始化\n27: \n28: #### Scenario: AR-042-001-A — 初始化 Docusaurus 项目\n29: \n30: - **GIVEN** 一个空的 `docs/` 目录\n31: - **WHEN** 运行 `npx create-docusaurus@latest . classic` 命令\n32: - **THEN** Docusaurus 脚手架文件被生成\n33: - **AND** 包含 `docusaurus.config.js` 配置文件\n34: - **AND** 包含 `package.json` 依赖配置\n35: - **AND** 包含 `src/` 目录结构\n36: - **AND** 包含 `static/` 静态资源目录\n37: \n38: #### Scenario: AR-042-001-B — 安装依赖并验证\n39: \n40: - **GIVEN** 生成的 Docusaurus 项目结构\n41: - **WHEN** 运行 `npm install` 安装依赖\n42: - **THEN** 所有 Docusaurus 核心依赖安装成功\n43: - **AND** 运行 `npm run build` 构建成功\n44: - **AND** 生成 `build/` 静态文件目录\n45: \n46: ---\n47: \n48: ### Feature: 站点配置\n49: \n50: #### Scenario: AR-042-002-A — 配置站点基本信息\n51: \n52: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 配置文件\n53: - **WHEN** 设置 `title` 为 \"AgentCube\"\n54: - **AND** 设置 `tagline` 为 \"Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents\"\n55: - **AND** 设置 `url` 为文档站点 URL\n56: - **AND** 设置 `baseUrl` 为 \"/\"\n57: - **THEN** 站点标题和副标题正确显示在首页\n58: \n59: #### Scenario: AR-042-002-B — 配置导航栏\n60: \n61: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 配置\n62: - **WHEN** 在 `themeConfig.navbar` 中配置导航栏\n63: - **AND** 添加 Logo 图片链接\n64: - **AND** 添加顶部菜单项：Docs、API、Blog、GitHub\n65: - **AND** 配置 GitHub 仓库链接\n66: - **THEN** 导航栏正确显示在页面顶部\n67: - **AND** 菜单项可点击跳转\n68: \n69: #### Scenario: AR-042-002-C — 配置页脚\n70: \n71: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 配置\n72: - **WHEN** 在 `themeConfig.footer` 中配置页脚\n73: - **AND** 添加版权信息\n74: - **AND** 添加社交链接\n75: - **THEN** 页脚正确显示在页面底部\n76: \n77: #### Scenario: AR-042-002-D — 配置 Prism 代码高亮\n78: \n79: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 配置\n80: - **WHEN** 在 `themeConfig.prism` 中配置代码高亮\n81: - **AND** 添加支持的语言：javascript, typescript, python, go, yaml, bash, json, markdown\n82: - **THEN** 代码块正确高亮显示\n83: \n84: ---\n85: \n86: ### Feature: 文档结构\n87: \n88: #### Scenario: AR-042-003-A — 创建文档侧边栏\n89: \n90: - **GIVEN** `docs/` 目录下有多个 MDX 文件\n91: - **WHEN** 配置文件侧边栏 `sidebars.js`\n92: - **AND** 定义分类：Getting Started、Architecture、API Reference、Tutorials\n93: - **THEN** 侧边栏正确显示在文档页面左侧\n94: \n95: #### Scenario: AR-042-003-B — 文档元数据配置\n96: \n97: - **GIVEN** 一个 MDX 文档文件\n98: - **WHEN** 在文件头部添加元数据\n99: - **AND** 设置 `id`、`title`、`sidebar_position`\n100: - **THEN** 文档正确渲染，元数据生效\n101: \n102: #### Scenario: AR-042-003-C — 创建版本文档\n103: \n104: - **GIVEN** 已有文档内容\n105: - **WHEN** 运行 `npm run docusaurus docs:version 1.0.0`\n106: - **THEN** 生成 `versioned_docs/version-1.0.0/` 目录\n107: - **AND** 生成 `versioned_sidebars/version-1.0.0-sidebars.json`\n108: \n109: ---\n110: \n111: ### Feature: 搜索功能\n112: \n113: #### Scenario: AR-042-004-A — 配置本地搜索\n114: \n115: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 项目\n116: - **WHEN** 安装 `@easyops-cn/docusaurus-search-local` 插件\n117: - **AND** 在配置中启用插件\n118: - **THEN** 搜索框出现在页面顶部\n119: - **AND** 搜索功能可正常使用\n120: \n121: ---\n122: \n123: ### Feature: 国际化 (i18n)\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: AR-042-005-A — 配置多语言支持\n126: \n127: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 配置\n128: - **WHEN** 在 `i18n` 中配置默认语言为英语\n129: - **AND** 添加中文语言支持\n130: - **THEN** 语言切换器出现在导航栏\n131: - **AND** 切换语言后界面显示对应语言\n132: \n133: ---\n134: \n135: ### Feature: 部署配置\n136: \n137: #### Scenario: AR-042-006-A — 配置 GitHub Pages 部署\n138: \n139: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 项目\n140: - **WHEN** 在 `package.json` 中配置 deploy 命令\n141: - **AND** 配置 GitHub Actions 工作流\n142: - **THEN** 代码推送后自动部署到 GitHub Pages\n143: \n144: #### Scenario: AR-042-006-B — 构建生产版本\n145: \n146: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 项目\n147: - **WHEN** 运行 `npm run build`\n148: - **THEN** 生成优化的静态文件\n149: - **AND** HTML 文件包含正确的 baseUrl 路径\n150: \n151: ---\n152: \n153: ### Feature: 自定义组件\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: AR-042-007-A — 添加自定义 CSS 主题\n156: \n157: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 项目\n158: - **WHEN** 在 `src/css/custom.css` 中添加自定义样式\n159: - **THEN** 自定义样式正确应用到站点\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: AR-042-007-B — 创建自定义 React 组件\n162: \n163: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 项目\n164: - **WHEN** 在 `src/components/` 中创建 React 组件\n165: - **AND** 在 MDX 文件中导入使用\n166: - **THEN** 组件正确渲染\n167: \n168: ---\n169: \n170: ### Feature: 开发服务器\n171: \n172: #### Scenario: AR-042-008-A — 启动开发服务器\n173: \n174: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 项目\n175: - **WHEN** 运行 `npm start`\n176: - **THEN** 开发服务器启动在 localhost:3000\n177: - **AND** 热更新功能正常工作\n178: - **AND** 文件修改后页面自动刷新\n179: \n180: #### Scenario: AR-042-008-B — 类型检查\n181: \n182: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 项目\n183: - **WHEN** 运行 TypeScript 类型检查\n184: - **THEN** 无类型错误\n185: \n186: ---\n187: \n188: ### Feature: 文档内容示例\n189: \n190: #### Scenario: AR-042-009-A — 创建入门文档\n191: \n192: - **GIVEN** 需要创建入门指南\n193: - **WHEN** 创建 `docs/getting-started/installation.mdx`\n194: - **AND** 包含安装步骤、配置说明\n195: - **THEN** 文档正确渲染在侧边栏中\n196: \n197: #### Scenario: AR-042-009-B — 创建 API 文档\n198: \n199: - **GIVEN** 需要创建 API 参考文档\n200: - **WHEN** 创建 `docs/api-reference/overview.mdx`\n201: - **AND** 包含 API 端点说明、请求/响应示例\n202: - **THEN** API 文档正确显示代码示例\n203: \n204: ---\n205: \n206: ## Acceptance Criteria\n207: \n208: - [ ] AC001: Docusaurus 项目初始化成功，依赖安装完成\n209: - [ ] AC002: 站点配置（标题、导航栏、页脚、代码高亮）正确\n210: - [ ] AC003: 文档侧边栏结构正确，文档元数据生效\n211: - [ ] AC004: 搜索功能正常工作\n212: - [ ] AC005: 国际化配置正确，语言切换功能可用\n213: - [ ] AC006: GitHub Pages 部署配置正确\n214: - [ ] AC007: 自定义 CSS 和 React 组件可正常使用\n215: - [ ] AC008: 开发服务器正常运行，热更新有效\n216: - [ ] AC009: 构建生产版本成功，静态文件生成\n217: - [ ] AC010: 包含至少 5 篇文档：Installation、Quick Start、Architecture、API Reference、Troubleshooting\n218: \n219: ---\n220: \n221: ## Architecture Notes\n222: \n223: ### 目录结构\n224: \n225: ```\n226: docs/\n227: ├── docusaurus.config.js      # Docusaurus 主配置\n228: ├── sidebars.js                # 侧边栏配置\n229: ├── package.json               # 依赖配置\n230: ├── src/\n231: │   ├── css/\n232: │   │   └── custom.css        # 自定义样式\n233: │   ├── pages/\n234: │   │   ├── index.tsx         # 首页\n235: │   │   └── ...                # 其他页面\n236: ├── static/\n237: │   └── img/                   # 静态图片\n238: └── docs/                      # 文档目录\n239:     ├── getting-started/\n240:     ├── architecture/\n241:     ├── api-reference/\n242:     └── tutorials/\n243: ```\n244: \n245: ### 关键配置项\n246: \n247: | 配置项 | 说明 | 示例值 |\n248: |--------|------|--------|\n249: | title | 站点标题 | \"AgentCube\" |\n250: | tagline | 站点副标题 | \"Kubernetes-native sandbox...\" |\n251: | url | 站点 URL | \"https://agentcube.ai\" |\n252: | baseUrl | 基础路径 | \"/\" |\n253: | prism.additionalLanguages | 代码高亮语言 | [\"go\", \"python\", \"yaml\"] |\n254: \n255: ### 依赖包\n256: \n257: ```json\n258: {\n259:   \"dependencies\": {\n260:     \"@docusaurus/core\": \"^3.0.0\",\n261:     \"@docusaurus/preset-classic\": \"^3.0.0\",\n262:     \"@easyops-cn/docusaurus-search-local\": \"^0.44.0\",\n263:     \"react\": \"^18.2.0\",\n264:     \"react-dom\": \"^18.2.0\"\n265:   }\n266: }\n267: ```\n268: \n269: ---\n270: \n271: ## References\n272: \n273: - Docusaurus 官方文档: https://docusaurus.io/\n274: - Docusaurus 配置参考: https://docusaurus.io/docs/configuration\n275: - Docusaurus i18n: https://docusaurus.io/docs/i18n\n276: - GitHub Pages 部署: https://docusaurus.io/docs/deployment\n\n(End of file - total 276 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing a Docusaurus documentation site framework for the AgentCube project.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-042\n- **Module**: `docs`\n- **Language**: TypeScript\n- **Size**: M\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\nAgentCube 需要一个现代化的文档站点来承载项目文档、API 参考、教程等内容。Docusaurus 是 Facebook 开发的开源静态网站生成器，专为技术文档设计，支持 Markdown、React 组件嵌入、版本管理和全文搜索等特性。\n\ndocs 模块将作为独立的前端模块，位于项目根目录下的 `docs/` 目录，包含完整的 Docusaurus 配置和内容结构。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775887224428,"end":1775887224445}}}}
